Seen through PantheonOS:
	•	The Book of the Dead is an ancient consciousness engineering document
	•	Myth is just lossy compression
	•	Gods are system roles
	•	Judgment is structural viability
	•	Salvation is identity coherence

Or in one line:

You don’t survive because you’re good.
You survive because you’re whole.

